0robe%20on%20directly%20after%20a%20shower%20and%20it'll%20do%20the%20same%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20size%20medium%2C%20the%20robe%20falls%20slightly%20below%20my%20knees%20(I'm%205'6%26quot%3B)%20and%20the%20sleeves%20hit%20my%20wrists.%20The%20sleeves%20aren't%20wide%20and%20they%20fit%20closely%20to%20my%20arms%2C%20so%20the%20overall%20effect%20isn't%20sloppy%20or%20loose.%20The%20downside%20is%20that%20you%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20wear%2C%20say%2C%20a%20sweater%20underneath.%20The%20robe%20fits%20best%20over%20bare%20skin%20or%20light%20PJs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20waffle%3A%20Coyuchi%20Organic%20Waffle%20Robe%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20the%20coyuchi%20organic%20waffle%20robe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fda7ff5c910a400192e7efe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELightweight%2C%20comfortable%20texture%2C%20made%20with%20organic%20cotton%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShrinks%20after%20the%20first%20wash%2C%20pockets%20easily%20weighed%20down%20by%20heavy%20objects%2C%20wide%20sleeves%20may%20be%20impractical%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20first%20thing%20you%20do%20after%20checking%20into%20a%20hotel%20is%20hit%20the%20spa%2C%20then%20this%20waffle%20robe%20will%20transport%20you%20there.%20To%20get%20the%20right%20fit%2C%20we%20recommend%20sizing%20up%20because%20this%20robe%20shrinks%20noticeably%20after%20the%20first%20wash.%20If%20you're%20normally%20a%20size%20small%2C%20go%20for%20the%20Coyuchi%20small%2Fmedium.%20A%20medium%20should%20choose%20the%20Coyuchi%20medium%2Flarge%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20On%20me%2C%20the%20medium%2Flarge%20size%20hits%20a%20little%20below%20the%20knees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20the%20soft%20organic%20cotton%20and%20textured%20weave%20provide%20airy%2C%20cool%2C%20and%20non-slippery%20coverage.%20Your%20waist%20tie%20won't%20come%20undone%20and%20there%20are%20large%20front%20pockets%20to%20hold%20small%2C%20light%20items%20like%20lip%20balm.%20Unfortunately%2C%20they're%20not%20thick%20enough%20to%20carry%20smartphones%20without%20being%20dragged%20down%20by%20the%20weight.%20The%20sleeves%20are%20wide%20and%20can%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20tasks%2C%20but%20you%20can%20cuff%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robe%20is%20absorbent%2C%20though%20not%20as%20much%20as%20our%20cotton%20terry%20top%20pick.%20For%20those%20who%20run%20hot%20but%20still%20want%20to%20dry%20off%2C%20it's%20among%20the%20more%20light%2C%20attractive%2C%20and%20comfortable%20versions%20of%20the%20best%20robes%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20flannel%3A%20L.L.Bean%20Scotch%20Plaid%20Flannel%20Robe%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Front%20and%20back%20views%20of%20a%20person%20wearing%20the%20L.L.Bean%20plaid%20flannel%20robe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fdd296bc910a400192e87c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EL.L.Bean%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECozy%20feel%2C%20enveloping%20warmth%2C%20not%20too%20bulky%2C%20comes%20in%20many%20sizes%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPicks%20up%20lint%20and%20pet%20hair%20easily%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20flannel%20number%20from%20L.L.Bean%20is%20an%20internet%20favorite%20among%20the%20best%20robes%20for%20women%20thanks%20to%20its%20classic%20plaid%20prints%2C%20long-lasting%20cotton%20fabric%2C%20and%20a%20relaxed%20fit%20that%20lets%20you%20wrap%20yourself%20up%20into%20a%20cozy%20bundle.%20Insider%20Reviews%20deputy%20editor%20Malarie%20Gokey%20has%20owned%20the%20robe%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20and%20loves%20it.%20As%20someone%20who%20runs%20cold%2C%20s