nce%20its%20luxury%20around%20the%20house%20for%20significantly%20less.%20The%20100%25%20Mongolian%20cashmere%20robe%20has%20a%20basic%20kimono%20design%20with%20a%20wait%20tie%20closure%20and%20two%20front%20patch%20pockets.%20The%20material%20is%20beautifully%20soft%2C%20and%20feels%20insulating%20despite%20being%20thin.%20I%20styled%20it%20over%20a%20cami%20and%20sleep%20shorts%2C%20and%20still%20felt%20warm%20enough%20on%20a%20chilly%20fall%20morning.%20It%20can%20even%20easily%20pass%20as%20a%20long%20cardigan%20if%20you%20take%20out%20its%20waist%20tie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShedding%20is%20natural%20with%20new%20cashmere%2C%20and%20because%20I%20chose%20black%2C%20it%20was%20immediately%20noticeable%20on%20my%20first%20wear.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20wears%2C%20the%20excess%20fibers%20thinned%20out%20and%20it%20was%20smooth%20enough%20to%20wear%20on%20bare%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20wear%20this%20first%20thing%20out%20of%20the%20shower%2C%20because%20even%20though%20it%20can%20handle%20some%20sweat%2C%20cashmere%20doesn't%20absorb%20water%20as%20well%20as%20terry%20cloth.%20It's%20best%20suited%20as%20a%20cozy%20robe%20to%20lounge%20or%20work%20from%20home%20in.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Gabrielle%20Chase%2C%20Style%20%26amp%3B%20Beauty%20Updates%20Fellow%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fquince-cashmere-review%5C%22%3EQuince%20cashmere%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20should%20I%20look%20for%20in%20a%20bathrobe%3F%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20features%20to%20consider%20as%20you%20shop%20for%20the%20best%20robe%2C%20including%20style%2C%20fabric%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20durability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20kimono-style%20design%20is%20the%20standard.%20%26quot%3BKimono%20robes%20offer%20a%20classic%20tailored%20fit%2C%20with%20wrist-length%20sleeves%2C%20and%20have%20a%20streamlined%20flat%20collar%2C%26quot%3B%20Nuboer%2