get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Network%20Open%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20Stanford%20University%20looked%20at%2022%20sets%20of%20identical%20twins%2C%20healthy%20adults%20averaging%2040%20years%20old%2C%20as%20they%20underwent%20an%20eight-week%20diet%20experiment.%20One%20member%20of%20each%20pair%20of%20twins%20was%20randomly%20assigned%20a%20vegan%20diet%2C%20eating%20exclusively%20plant-based%20foods%20with%20no%20meat%2C%20eggs%2C%20dairy%2C%20or%20other%20animal%20products.%20The%20other%20twin%20in%20each%20pair%20was%20assigned%20an%20omnivorous%20diet%2C%20including%20at%20least%20one%20serving%20of%20fish%2C%20meat%20or%20chicken%2C%20one%20egg%2C%20and%20a%20serving%20and%20a%20half%20of%20dairy%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20diets%20were%20designed%20to%20be%20nutritionally%20balanced%20and%20full%20of%20veggies%2C%20beans%2C%20and%20whole%20grains%2C%20without%20added%20sugars%20or%20other%20refined%20carbs.%20The%20food%20was%20provided%20at%20no%20cost%20to%20participants%20by%20a%20meal%20delivery%20service%20for%20the%20first%20four%20weeks%2C%20after%20which%20participants%20prepared%20their%20own%20meals%20and%20snacks%2C%20with%20guidance%20from%20an%20on-call%20dietitian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20participants%20on%20the%20vegan%20diet%20had%20lower%20cholesterol%20and%20insulin%20levels%20and%20lost%20more%20weight%20than%20their%20meat-eating%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20interesting%20part%20of%20the%20study%26quot%3B%20was%20that%20the%20vegans%20were%20also%20biologically%20younger%20based%20on%20markers%20of%20health%2C%20according%20to%20Christopher%20Gardner%2C%20senior%20author%20of%20the%20study%20and%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20Stanford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20these%20results%20and%20thinking%20about%20longevity%2C%20most%20of%20us%20would%20benefit%20from%20going%20to%20a%20more%20plant-based%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-biological-age-is-reverse-aging-possible-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiological%20age%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20to%20reverse%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20hot%20trend%20in%20healthcare%2C%20but%20measuring%20it%20can%20be%20complex%20and%20sometimes%20controversial%20Business%20Insider's%20Hilary%20Brueck%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditional%20evidence%20has%20suggested%20that%20plant-based%20eating%20habits%20are%20linked%20to%20healthier%20aging%2C%20and%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fplant-based-mediterranean-diet-add-ten-years-longevity-modeling-study-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadd%20years%20to%20your%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20plenty%20of%20studies%20have%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Feating-less-meat-vegan-vegetarian-linked-lower-cancer-risk-study-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompare%20vegan%20and%20omnivore%20diets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20other%20variable%20can%20skew%20the%20results%2C%20such%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20vegans%20may%20be%20more%20health%20conscious%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20or%20have%20different%20socioeconomic%20backgrounds%20or%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20twins%20allowed%20the%20study%20to%20uniquely%20account%20for%20variables%20such%20as%20genetics%20and%20upbringing%2C%20invaluable%20data%20that%20also%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20fun%2C%20Gardner%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20did%20this%20study%20provide%20a%20groundbreaking%20way%20to%20assert%20that%20a%20vegan%20diet%20is%20healthier%20than%20the%20conventional%20omnivore%20diet%2C%20but%20the%20twins%20were%20also%20a%20riot%20to%20work%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20dressed%20the%20same%2C%20they%20talked%20the%20same%20and%20they%20had%20a%20banter%20between%20them%20that%20you%20could%20have%20only%20if%20you%20spent%20an%20inordinate%20amount%20of%20time%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20may%20not%20have%20to%20go%20fully%20vegan%20for%20better%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20but%20one%20of%20the%20vegan%20twins%20were%20able%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20diet%20throughout%20the%20study%2C%20suggesting%20it%20could%20be%20an%20accessible%20way%20for%20people%20to%20learn%20to%20eat%20more%20healthfully%2C%20Gardner%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbodybuilder-dietitian-shares-tips-for-eating-protein-to-build-muscle-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainability%20is%20key%20for%20a%20healthy%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20you'll%20only%20benefit%20from%20an%20eating%20plan%20if%20you%20can%20continue%20following%20it%20long-term%2C%20dietitians%20have%20previously%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20vegan%20participants%20self-reported%20that%20they%20weren't%20as%20happy%20with%20their%20food%2C%20which%20could%20account%20for%20the%20extra%20weight%20loss.%20And%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIvXo-RQGdls%26embeds_referring_euri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmed.stanford.edu%252F%26source_ve_path%3DMjM4NTE%26feature%3Demb_title%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efollow-up%20interview%20at%20Stanford%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20not%20all%20of%20them%20opted%20to%20remain%20vegan%20after%20the%20study%20%E2%80%94%20one%20mentioned%20she%20transitioned%20to%20vegetarianism%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20trying%20to%20eat%20more%20beans%2C%20whole%20grains%2C%20veggies%2C%20and%20nuts%20could%20pay%20off%20for%20your%20long-term%20health%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20swear%20off%20animal-based%20foods%20completely%2C%20according%20to%20Gardner%2C%20who%20said%20he%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20vegan%26quot%3B%