20acts%20of%20kindness%20that%20people%20can%20do%20to%20express%20their%20love%20for%20their%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20it%20because%20they%20know%20it%20makes%20both%20of%20their%20lives%20easier%20and%20promotes%20gross%20domestic%20happiness%20in%20the%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Max%20Alley%2C%20an%20online%20dating%20coach%20who%20runs%20Match%20Up%20Online%20Dating%20Coaching%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlley%20added%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20test%20is%20a%20useful%20measure%20for%20how%20strong%20a%20relationship%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20it's%20an%20accurate%20measure%20of%20love%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%2C%20does%20a%20partner%20consistently%20want%20to%20be%20helpful%20or%20do%20little%20acts%20of%20kindness%20to%20make%20their%20partner%20feel%20good%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrice%20Le%20Goy%2C%20a%20marriage%20and%20family%20therapist%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20agreed%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20we%20often%20think%20of%20big%2C%20grand%20gestures%20when%20we%20think%20of%20romantic%20acts%2C%20it's%20actually%20the%20regular%20daily%20interactions%20with%20our%20partner%20that%20makes%20us%20feel%20close%20to%20them%20and%20cared%20for%20by%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it's%20a%20small%20act%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20caring%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20partner%20knows%20it's%20a%20task%20you%20dread%2C%26quot%3B%20Le%20Goy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-trends-viral-videos-influence-over-companies-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20most%20trends%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20test%20only%20goes%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20%26quot%3Bopens%20the%20door%20to%20questioning%20what%20your%20core%20values%20are%20and%20if%20they're%20matched%20with%20somebody%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amy%20Nobile%2C%20a%20dating%20coach%20in%20New%20York%20City%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Love%2C%20Amy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20to%20go%20deeper%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat%20bar%20is%20pretty%20low%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20have%20a%20higher%20standard%20than%20asking%20our%20partner%20to%20peel%20an%20orange%20for%20us.%20There's%20no%20way%20that%20correlates%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fearly-signs-of-good-relationship-according-to-therapist-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20of%20the%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20just%20as%20important%20to%20be%20able%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20is%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Byes%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20request%20from%20your%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20say%20no%20when%20there's%20a%20good%20reason%20for%20it%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20strong%20relationship%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthe-right-way-to-set-boundaries-with-people-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20boundaries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Le%20Goy%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20feel%20like%20they%20always%20need%20to%20say%20yes%20and%20meet%20others'%20needs%20before%20meeting%20their%20own%2C%20that%20may%20be%20them%20communicating%20that%20they%20feel%20less%20than%20equal%20or%20unworthy%20of%20their%20partner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forange-peel-theory-tiktok-relationship-test-dating-experts-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701465139000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a379958e7c0c29a28e273%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forange-peel-theory-tiktok-relationship-test-dating-experts-2023-1