0skyrocketed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israeli%20forces%20bomb%20what%20it%20says%20are%20Hamas%20targets%20in%20November.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a021158e7c0c29a28b93b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221590%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20forces%20bombing%20what%20it%20says%20are%20Hamas%20targets%20in%20November.%3Cp%3EScreengrab%20via%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20it%20figure%20out%20which%20targets%20to%20strike%20in%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20IDF%20relies%20on%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Btarget%20factory%26quot%3B%20powered%20by%20an%20AI%20system%20that%20produces%20recommendations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20several%20years%20old%2C%20the%20operation%20was%20created%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%C2%A0available%20Hamas%20targets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week-long%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20ended%20Friday%20morning%20local%20time%20after%20the%20militant%20group%20was%20accused%20of%20violating%20the%20agreement.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20said%20that%20in%20the%20hours%20since%2C%20it%20has%20already%20struck%20over%20200%20targets%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resumption%20of%20fighting%20indicates%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20the%20war%20and%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20Israel's%20bombardment%20of%20the%20besieged%20coastal%20enclave%20will%20proceed.%20Prior%20to%20the%20ceasefire%2C%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20triggered%20global%20backlash%2C%20and%20statements%20from%20the%20military%20and%20new%20reports%20published%20this%20week%20are%20revealing%20details%20about%20the%20military's%20relatively%20little-known%20targeting%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20a%20month%20of%20war%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20revealed%20that%20it%20was%20relying%20on%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20system%20to%20help%20determine%20where%20in%20Gaza%20it%20should%20bomb.%20It's%20part%20of%20an%20operation%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Btarget%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20strike%20locations%20available%20to%20the%20military%20by%20over%2070%2C000%20percent%20since%20the%20system%20first%20became%20functional%20several%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btarget%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20more%20officially%20the%20Targeting%20Directorate%2C%20is%20a%20unit%20staffed%20by%20officers%20and%20soldiers%20who%20are%20tasked%20with%20cybersecurity%2C%20decoding%2C%20and%20research.%20It%20first%20began%20operating%20in%202019%20as%20a%20way%20to%20find%20and%20identify%20more%20Hamas%20targets%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20During%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20it%20has%20worked%20with%20other%20intelligence%20units%20across%20the%20Israeli%20military%20to%20quickly%20find%20targets%20so%20strikes%20can%20then%20be%20carried%20out%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221266%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20rises%20above%20buildings%20during%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20Rafah%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20December%201%2C%202023%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a390c58e7c0c29a28e351%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20above%20buildings%20during%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20Rafah%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20December%201%2C%202023%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20SAID%20KHATIB%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20plan%20to%20make%20intelligence%20fully%20accessible%20to%20the%20brigade%20and%20division%20levels%2C%20and%20to%20'close%20circles'%20immediately%2C%20with%20help%20from%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20IDF%20official%20said%20in%20a%20November%202%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2F%25D7%2590%25D7%25AA%25D7%25A8%25D7%2599-%25D7%2599%25D7%2597%25D7%2599%25D7%2593%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA%2F%25D7%2599%25D7%2595%25D7%259E%25D7%259F-%25D7%2594%25D7%259E%25D7%259C%25D7%2597%25D7%259E%25D7%2594%2F%25D7%259B%25D7%259C-%25D7%2594%25D7%259B%25D7%25AA%25D7%2591%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA%2F%25D7%2594%25D7%25A4%25D7%25A6%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA%2F%25D7%259E%25D7%259C%25D7%2597%25D7%259E%25D7%2594-%25D7%259E%25D7%2598%25D7%25A8%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA-%25D7%25A9%25D7%2594%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA%25D7%25A7%25D7%25A4%25D7%2595-%25D7%259B%25D7%2595%25D7%2597%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA-%25D7%25A6%25D7%2594-%25D7%259C-%25D7%2590%25D7%2592%25D7%25A3-%25D7%2594%25D7%259E%25D7%2595%25D7%2593%25D7%2599%25D7%25A2%25D7%2599%25D7%259F-%25D7%2597%25D7%2599%25D7%259C-%25D7%2594%25D7%2590%25D7%2595%25D7%2595%25D7%2599%25D7%25A8-%25D7%2597%25D7%2599%25D7%259C-%25D7%2594%25D7%2599%25D7%259D%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IDF%2C%20the%20AI%20system%20that%20powers%20the%20Targeting%20Directorate%20absorbs%20intelligence%20and%20rapidly%20produces%20recommended%20targets%20for%20a%20researcher%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20not%20just%20match%20but%20exceed%20what%20a%20human%20might%20otherwise%20suggest.%20The%20official%20stressed%20that%20the%20unit%20relies%20on%20a%20high%20standard%20for%20the%20targets%20that%20are%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20compromise%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20intelligence%20and%20produce%20targets%20for%20precise%20attacks%20on%20infrastructure%20associated%20with%20Hamas%2C%20inflicting%20great%20damage%20on%20the%20enemy%20and%20minimal%20harm%20to%20those%20not%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20IDF%20official%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20work%20without%20compromise%20when%20defining%20who%20and%20what%20the%20enemy%20is.%20Hamas%20terrorists%20are%20not%20immune%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20where%20they%20hide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20targeting%20program%20became%20operational%2C%20Israel%20could%20produce%2050%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20in%20a%20year%2C%20Aviv%20Kochavi%2C%20the%20former%20IDF%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20said%20in%20a%20June%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynetnews.com%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2Fry0uzlhu3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Israeli%20news%20outlet%20Ynet.%20But%20once%20the%20AI%20system%20was%20activated%20during%20the%202021%20Operation%20Guardian%20of%20the%20Walls%2C%20it%20could%20effectively%20generate%20as%20many%20as%20100%20targets%20in%20a%20single%20day%20%E2%80%94%20half%20of%20which%20would%20be%20attacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20air%20force%20fighter%20aircraft%20releases%20flares%20as%20it%20flies%20over%20along%20the%20border%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20near%20southern%20Israel%20on%20November%2012%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a38ba47f9ecb37d893fe6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli%20air%20force%20fighter%20aircraft%20releases%20flares%20as%20it%20flies%20over%20along%20the%20border%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20near%20southern%20Israel%20on%20November%2012%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20MENAHEM%20KAHANA%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20said%20in%20the%20early%20November%20statement%20that%20the%20Targeting%20Directorate%20was%20working%20%26quot%3Baround%20the%20clock%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20struck%20over%2012%2C000%20targets%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bthousands%26quot%3B%20more%20identified%2C%20in%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20the%20war.%20Nearly%20a%20month%20later%2C%20it's%20unclear%20exactly%20how%20much%20that%20figure%20has%20grown%2C%20although%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20significantly%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20investigation%20by%20%2B972%20Magazine%20and%20Local%20Call%2C%20a%20Hebrew-language%20site%2C%20into%20the%20intense%20Israeli%20bombing%20campaign%20of%20Gaza%20describes%20how%20AI%20contributes%20to%20the%20extensive%20targeting%2C%20which%20has%20leveled%20entire%20neighborhoods%20in%20the%20coastal%20enclave%20and%20killed%20nearly%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fmiddleeast%2Flive-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-news-12-1-23%2Fh_f75c46103644118cb2fbd5694be82d6e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Hamas-run%20health%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fmass-assassination-factory-israel-calculated-bombing-gaza%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20published%20on%20Thursday%2C%20cites%20Israeli%20intelligence%20sources%20in%20explaining%20that%20the%20AI%20system%20called%20%26quot%3BGospel%26quot%3B%20produces%20recommendations%20for%20targeting%20homes%20or%20areas%20where%20suspected%20Hamas%20or%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20militants%20might%20reside%2C%20which%20can%20then%20be%20hit%20with%20airstrikes.%20Sources%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20knows%20in%20advance%20how%20many%20civilians%20might%20be%20killed%20in%20attacks%20on%20residences%2C%20and%20strikes%20are%20determined%20based%20on%20assessments%20of%20the%20potential%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20Israeli%20intelligence%20officer%20told%20the%20outlets%20that%20the%20Gospel%20system%20creates%20a%20%26quot%3Bmass%20assassination%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20%26quot%3Bquantity%20and%20not%20on%20quality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20aftermath%20of%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Gaza%20on%20December%201%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a399747f9ecb37d894060%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Gaza%20on%20December%201%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Fadi%20Alwhidi%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20exactly%20what%20data%20and%20intelligence%20goes%20into%20the%20AI%20system.%20The%20IDF%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20queries%20about%20how%20the%20system%20determines%20who%20is%20and%20isn't%20a%20Hamas%20militant%2C%20what%20human%20checks%20are%20in%20place%20on%20the%20targeting%20program%2C%20or%20how%20many%20militants%20and%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20AI%20assessments%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20use%20of%20AI%20is%20not%20necessarily%20a%20new%20concept%20in%20warfare.%20There%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F07%2F26%2Fdrones-ai-ukraine-war-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexamples%20of%20its%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20the%20US%20and%20China%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-closer-ai-drones-autonomously-decide-kill-humans-artifical-intelligence-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20select%20targets%20autonomously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2050%20countries%20have%20endorsed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fpolitical-declaration-on-responsible-military-use-of-artificial-intelligence-and-autonomy%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLaunched%2520in%2520February%25202023%2520at%2Cand%2520use%2520of%2520military%2520AI.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclaration%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20responsible%20use%20of%20AI%20and%20autonomy%20for%20military%20purposes%20that%20was%20launched%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.g