already%20out%20of%20the%20bottle%20with%20the%20release%20of%20numerous%20AI%20tools%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kochavi%2C%20the%20former%20IDF%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlongside%20the%20immense%20potential%20and%20tremendous%20contribution%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20humanity%2C%20it%20is%20capable%20of%20replacing%20and%20even%20alienating%20humans%20from%20decision-making%20altogether%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20decisions%20about%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Deep%20Cleaned%20Video%20Fellow%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAlisa%20Kaff%20provided%20translations%20for%20this%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-lets-ai-decide-what-it-should-bomb-increasing-the-number-of-targets-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701464573000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a367886933e8fdb2ef78f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-lets-ai-decide-what-it-should-bomb-increasing-the-number-of-targets-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20relied%20on%20an%20AI%20system%20to%20produce%20Hamas-affiliated%20targets%20that%20it%20can%20bomb%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-lets-ai-decide-what-it-should-bomb-increasing-the-number-of-targets-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Red%20Sea%20Film%20Foundation%20Drives%20African%20and%20Arab%20Films%2C%20Like%20%E2%80%98Four%20Daughters%2C%E2%80%99%20as%20Well%20as%20Hollywood%20Movies%2C%20Like%20%E2%80%98Ferrari%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701464438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fv