S%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Peskov%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Russian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussian-crude-exports-output-pledge-opec-crude-oil-prices-demand-2023-11%5C%22%3Eoil%20exports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20climbed%20despite%20the%20price%20cap%2C%20as%20its%20enforcement%20has%20proved%20challenging.%20The%20US%20Treasury%20Department%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fgreece-ship-avoiding-russia-oil-price-cap-west-sanctions-2023-11%5C%22%3Estepped%20up%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20sanctions%20against%20two%20firms%20that%20violated%20the%20cap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-sanctions-ukraine-energy-exports-oil-gas-price-cap-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701461429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a274758e7c0c29a28d541%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussian-sanctions-ukraine-energy-exports-oil-gas-price-cap-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Limiting%20Russia's%20energy%20revenue%20will%20ensure%20that%20Moscow%20can't%20rearm%20for%20future%20aggression%2C%20Geoffrey%20Pyatt%20told%20the%20Financial%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A108%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussian-sanctions-ukraine-energy-exports-oil-gas-price-cap-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bollywood%20Star%20Ranveer%20Singh%20Speaks%20About%20Reprising%20%E2%80%98Simbha%E2%80%99%20Role%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Binary%E2%80%99%20Between%20Theatrical%20and%20Streaming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701461355000%2C%22visu