%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20met%20Brazilian%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%2C%20British%20Foreign%20Secretary%20David%20Cameron%2C%20former%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Tony%20Blair%2C%20Turkey%20President%20RT%20Erdogan%2C%20Swedish%20Prime%20Minister%20Ulf%20Kristersson%20and%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20among%20other%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20a%20packed%20day-long%20schedule%20as%20he%20addressed%20the%20four%20sessions%20at%20the%20UN%20climate%20change%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20discuss%20ways%20to%20promote%20clean%20and%20green%20growth%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20said.%20Issues%20of%20bilateral%20and%20regional%20interests%20were%20also%20discussed%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20many%20leaders%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20Mr%20Kwatra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20climate%20negotiations%20largely%20avoided%20mentioning%20fossil%20fuels%20for%20decades%2C%20until%20Glasgow's%20COP26%20agreed%20to%20%26quot%3Bphasedown%26quot%3B%20unfiltered%20coal%20power%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bphase-out%20of%20inefficient%20fossil%20fuel%20subsidies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMomentum%20has%20built%20since%20then%20on%20a%20more%20ambitious%20pledge%20to%20move%20away%20from%20all%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20and%20the%20UN's%20former%20climate%20chief%20Christiana%20Figueres%20said%20an%20unprecedented%20surge%20in%20renewables%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20gave%20her%20optimism%20that%20the%20world%20can%20still%20achieve%20its%20climate%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20centre%20on%20the%202015%20Paris%20deal%2C%20which%20saw%20nearly%20200%20nations%20agree%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%20%26quot%3Bwell%20below%26quot%3B%20two%20degree%20Celsius%20since%20the%20pre-industrial%20era%2C%20and%20preferably%20a%20safer%20threshold%20of%201.5%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20COP28%20speech%20on%20Friday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20called%20on%20all%20nations%20to%20work%20together%20to%20cut%20global%20emissions%20drastically%2C%20and%20announced%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20credit%26quot%3B%20initiative%20that%20focuses%20on%20creating%20carbon%20skins%20with%20people's%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India's%20emissions%20are%20very%20low%20compared%20to%20other%20nations%20whose%20population%20is%20much%20less.%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20population%20is%2017%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20population%2C%20but%20in%20global%20carbon%20emissions%20India%20is%20only%20at%204%20per%20cent.%20We%20are%20moving%20fast%20in%20achieving%20the%20NDC%20targets.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20reached%20our%20non-fossil%20fuel%20targets%20nine%20years%20before%20the%20deadline%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Nationally%20Determined%20Contribution%20(NDC)%2C%20a%20climate%20action%20plan%20to%20cut%20emissions%20and%20adapt%20to%20climate%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20much%20time%20to%20correct%20the%20mistakes%20of%20the%20last%20century%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20and%20asked%20every%20nation%20to%20work%20sincerely%20to%20meet%20their%20NDC%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701454500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fp1ip53kg_pm-modi-italy-pm-selfie_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-melonis-selfie-with-pm-modi-at-cop28-4625913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Italy's%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20posted%20a%20selfie%20with%20her%20Indian%20counterpart%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP28%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-melonis-selfie-with-pm-modi-at-cop28-4625913%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-melonis-selfie-with-pm-modi-at-cop28-4625913%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fitaly-pm-giorgia-melonis-selfie-with-pm-modi-at-cop28-4625913%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Cops%20To%20Search%20Central%20Probe%20Agency%20Offices%20In%20Bribe%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Police%20have%20arrested%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fenforcement-directorate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E%20officer%20in%20Madurai%20for%20allegedly%20extorting%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20in%20cash%20from%20a%20state%20government%20employee.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20investigation%2C%20police%20are%20searching%20the%20central%20agency's%20offices%20in%20the%20city%20and%20the%20officer's%20residence%2C%20and%20have%20seized%20several%20documents.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20arrested%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20in%20question%20-%20Ankit%20Tiwari%20-%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20till%20December%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20not%20responded%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari%20originally%20demanded%20Rs%203%20crore%20to%20%26quot%3Bavert%20legal%20action%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20case%20that%20had%20already%20been%20settled.%20He%20contacted%20the%20employee%20on%20October%2029%2C%20claimed%20he%20was%20acting%20on%20instructions%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20and%20summoned%20him%20to%20the%20agency's%20Madurai%20office.%20When%20he%20came%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari%20accosted%20him%20and%20demanded%20the%20Rs%203%20crore%20bribe%2C%20which%20he%20later%20brought%20down%20to%20Rs%2051%20lakh%20claiming%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bspoken%20to%20his%20superiors%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20installment%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20was%20paid%20on%20November%201.%20The%20government%20employee%20was%20subsequently%20harassed%20by%20Mr%20Tiwari%20for%20the%20remaining%20Rs%2031%20lakh.%20On%20November%2030%20he%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20DVAC%20and%2C%20at%2010.30%20am%20today%20Friday%2C%20the%20department%20arrested%20Ankit%20Tiwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDVAC%20sources%C2%A0told%20NDTV%20Mr%20Tiwari%20was%20caught%20%26quot%3Bred-handed%26quot%3B%20following%20a%20high-speed%20car%20chase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DVAC%20is%20also%20investigating%20if%20Mr%20Tiwari%20received%20money%20from%20threatening%20or%20blackmailing%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EState%20Vs%20ED%20In%20Madras%20High%20Court%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari's%20arrest%20comes%20as%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20and%20the%20central%20investigative%20agency%20are%20at%20loggerheads%20over%20the%20latter's%20summons%20to%20five%20district%20collectors%3B%20this%20is%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20probe%20into%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20linked%20to%20illegal%20sand%20mining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20moment%20of%20relief%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin's%20administration%2C%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20this%20week%20stayed%20the%20summons%20for%20three%20weeks.%20It%20did%20not%2C%20though%2C%20stay%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summoned%20collectors%20-%20from%20the%20Ariyalur%2C%20Vellore%2C%20Thanjavur%2C%20Karur%20and%20Tiruchirapalli%20districts%20-%20and%20the%20state%20government%20have%20been%20given%20three%20weeks%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-summons-to-5-tamil-nadu-officers-stayed-by-madras-high-court-4612959%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCompletely%20Illegal%26quot%3B%3A%20Probe%20Agency%20Summons%20To%205%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Officers%20Paused%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%2C%20though%2C%20had%20argued%20the%20ED%20does%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20make%20such%20demands%20and%20that%20its%20summons%20to%20the%20five%20collectors%20is%20against%20the%20spirit%20of%20federalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20argued%20the%20central%20agency%20ought%20to%20seek%20such%20details%2C%20if%20needed%2C%20only%20via%20the%20state%20government%2C%20and%20that%20it%20could%20not%20conduct%20an%20inquiry%20without%20the%20latter's%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20survey%20by%20an%20expert%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsand-mining-in-tamil-nadu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EED%20claimed%20illegal%20sand%20mining%20worth%20Rs%204%2C500%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20taken%20place%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EDMK%20Mouthpiece%20Slams%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20official's%20arrest%20comes%20on%20the%20day%20the%20ruling%20DMK's%20mouthpiece%2C%20Murasoli%2C%20accused%20the%20BJP%20that%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20using%20the%20agency%20to%20malign%20its%20image.%20The%20newspaper%20questioned%20the%20ED's%20claim%20of%20corruption%2C%20challenging%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20alleged%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%26quot%3B%20figure%20and%20demanding%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20uses%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20create%20a%20black%20mark%20against%20DMK.%20ED%20said%20some%20random%20numbers...%20that%2C%20in%20two%20years%2C%20Rs%204%2C730%20crore%20of%20corruption%20was%20uncovered%20in%20sand%20mining.%20How%20do%20they%20know%20how%20much%20sand%20was%20in%20the%20river%20two%20years%20ago%3F%20They%20are%20just%20making%20up%20these%20numbers...%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Eagencie