title%22%3A%22EC%20Changes%20Counting%20Date%20for%20Mizoram%20Assembly%20Polls%20to%20December%204%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20Mizoram%20will%20be%20held%20on%20Monday%20(December%204)%2C%20instead%20of%20Sunday%20(December%203)%20as%20notified%20earlier%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20EC%2C%20the%20change%20is%20in%20response%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eseveral%20representations%20from%20various%20quarters%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Commission%20has%20received%20several%20representations%20from%20various%20quarters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Erequesting%20for%20change%20in%20the%20date%20of%20counting%20from%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%20December%203%2C%202023%20(Sunday)%20to%20some%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eother%20week%20day%2C%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDecember%203%2C%202023%2C%20being%20Sunday%20a%20special%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Esignificance%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Mizoram%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EC%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20the%20counting%20date%20will%20not%20affect%20other%20states%20where%20elections%20concluded%20recently.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%203%2C%20as%20announced%20earlier%2C%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmizoram-churches-pray-change-counting-date-assembly-polls%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20that%20churches%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2026%2C%20held%20special%20prayers%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Cdivine%20intervention%E2%80%9D%20to%20help%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20persuade%20the%20poll%20body%20to%20reschedule%20the%20counting%20date.%20Being%20a%20Christian-majority%20state%2C%20Mizoram%20considers%20Sunday%20solely%20as%20the%20day%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mizoram%20Kohhran%20Hruaitute%20Committee%20(MKHC)%2C%20a%20conglomerate%20of%2015%20major%20churches%20of%20the%20state%2C%20had%20also%20urged%20all%20churches%20this%20past%20Saturday%20(November%2025)%20to%20organise%20prayers%20during%20the%20Sunday%20church%20service%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20from%20God%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20counting%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20NGO%20Coordination%20Committee%20(NGOCC)%2C%20an%20Aizawl-based%20umbrella%20body%20of%20NGOs%20and%20student%20organisations%2C%20stayed%20put%20in%20New%20Delhi%20last%20week%20to%20seek%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20(CEC)%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20delegation%20came%20to%20the%20national%20Capital%20after%20pleas%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%20had%20gone%20unheard.%20Those%20pleas%20were%20made%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20CEC%20in%20New%20Delhi%20had%20announced%20the%20election%20schedule%20in%20the%20state%20along%20with%20December%203%20as%20the%20common%20date%20for%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20all%20the%20five%20poll-bound%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701448329000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-changes-counting-date-for-mizoram-assembly-polls-to-december-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Being%20a%20Christian-majority%20state%2C%20Mizoram%20considers%20Sun