e%20former%20did%20get%20strike%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20fourth%20over%2C%20he%20employed%20the%20cut%20shot%20off%20a%20Behrendorff%20delivery%20to%20open%20his%20account%20with%20a%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFastest%20to%204%2C000%20runs%20(by%20innings%20taken)%20in%20Men's%20T20%20cricket%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E107%20-%20Chris%20Gayle%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E113%20-%20Shaun%20Marsh%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E115%20-%20Babar%20Azam%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E116%20-%20Devon%20Conway%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E116%20-%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E117%20-%20KL%20Rahul%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20continued%20with%20his%20aggressive%20ways%20and%20played%20debutant%20spinner%20Chris%20Green%20through%20the%20off-side%20for%20a%20four%20before%20smashing%20him%20over%20the%20midwicket%20fence%20for%20a%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalled%20into%20the%20attack%20to%20stem%20the%20flow%20of%20runs%2C%20Hardie%20was%20hit%20straight%20down%20the%20ground%20for%20a%20four%20by%20Jaiswal%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20to%20bring%20him%20back%20ended%20in%20a%20success%20as%20Australia%20got%20their%20first%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20left-handed%20opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20for%20one%20too%20many%2C%20Jaiswal%20could%20not%20connect%20well%20enough%20and%20Ben%20McDermott%20completed%20a%20good%20catch%20running%20from%20mid-on%2C%20as%20India%20reached%2050%20for%20one%20at%20the%20end%20of%20powerplay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20the%20side%20after%20a%20small%20break%20following%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20vice-captain%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20(8)%2C%20looking%20to%20hit%20leg-spinner%20Tanveer%20Sangha%20out%20of%20the%20ground%2C%20could%20not%20get%20enough%20power%20or%20elevation%20and%20Green%20took%20the%20catch%20at%20long-on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20(1)%20casually%20edged%20Dwarshuis%20to%20the%20keeper%2C%20leaving%20India%20at%2063%20for%20three%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20ninth%20over%20and%20the%20crowd%20at%20Shaheed%20Veer%20Narayan%20Singh%20International%20Stadium%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partisan%20spectators%20were%20however%20not%20required%20to%20keep%20quiet%20for%20long%20as%20Rinku%20Singh%20got%20going%20straightaway%2C%20his%20customary%20powerful%20strokes%20aiding%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20and%20Ruturaj%20added%2048%20runs%20for%20the%20fourth%20wicket%20before%20the%20latter%20was%20dismissed%20by%20Sangha.%20But%20that%20did%20not%20deter%20Rinku%20from%20playing%20his%20natural%20game%20and%20he%20found%20an%20able%20ally%20in%20Jitesh%2C%20the%20two%20adding%2050%20runs%20in%20just%2029%20balls%20to%20lift%20India's%20run%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitesh%2C%20however%2C%20fell%20when%20he%20was%20looking%20good%20to%20add%20a%20few%20more%20runs%20to%20his%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701447720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffsq9g4ug_dfdf_625x300_01_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-makes-history-surpasses-kl-rahul-to-claim-sensational-t20-record-4625404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20surpassed%20KL%20Rahul%20to%20claim%20a%20brilliant%20record%20during%20the%20fourth%20T20I%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-makes-history-surpasses-kl-rahul-to-claim-sensational-t20-record-4625404%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-makes-history-surpasses-kl-rahul-to-claim-sensational-t20-record-4625404%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-makes-history-surpasses-kl-rahul-to-claim-sensational-t20-record-4625404%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22