3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20categorically%20stated%20that%20there%20is%20no%20change%20in%20any%20event%20or%20schedule%20of%20Assembly%20Elections%20of%20Mizoram%20or%20in%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20parties%20contesting%20the%20Mizoram%20election%20had%20asked%20for%20the%20date%20of%20counting%20to%20be%20shifted%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20from%20December%203%20to%20the%20next%20day%20and%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Brepresentations%20were%20made%20earlier%20but%20the%20Election%20Commission%20remained%20silent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPolitical%20parties%20in%20the%20fray%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20elections%20had%20asked%20for%20counting%20there%20to%20be%20shifted%20from%20Sunday%2C%20December%203rd%20to%20Monday%2C%20December%204th.%20Representations%20were%20made%20over%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20but%20the%20ECI%20remained%20silent.%20A%20little%20while%20earlier%2C%20it%20has%20shifted%20the%20date.%20Why%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1730609390183403938%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20states%20-%20Mizoram%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana%20went%20to%20polls%2C%20which%20is%20being%20viewed%20as%20the%20semi-final%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Voting%20in%20Mizoram%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%207.%20Mizoram%20has%2040%20Assembly%20seats%20and%20the%20majority%20mark%20is%2021.%20Counting%20in%20other%20states%20will%20be%20as%20per%20schedule%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20is%20expected%20to%20witness%20a%20high-stakes%20close%20battle%20between%20the%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20founded%20by%20former%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20Lalduhoma%20and%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20of%20Zoramthanga%2C%20who%20was%20once%20a%20leader%20of%20an%20insurgent%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ZPM%20was%20formed%20by%20merging%20six%20parties%20to%20take%20on%20Zoramthanga%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20was%20a%20guerilla%20fighting%20the%20Indian%20military%20before%20joining%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga's%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20is%20in%20a%20close-fight%20with%20the%20ZPM.%20The%20incumbent%20MNF%20government%20is%20hoping%20to%20stay%20in%20power%2C%20while%20the%20ZPM%20may%20give%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20MNF%2C%20NDTV's%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20suggested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20Chief%20Minister%20Zoramthanga%20has%20exuded%20confidence%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20hung%20assembly%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20we%20will%20form%20the%20government.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV's%20Poll%20of%20Polls%20suggest%20that%20the%20ZPM%20may%20win%2017%20seats%2C%20taking%20a%20lead%20against%20the%20MNF%20which%20is%20projected%20to%20get%2014%20seats%20in%20the%2040-member%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20projected%20to%20win%20seven%20seats%20and%20could%20be%20a%20king-maker%20in%20the%20close%20contest%20of%20Mizoram.%20All%20the%20exit%20polls%20for%20Mizoram%20gave%20the%20BJP%20a%20maximum%20of%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarning%3A%20Exit%20Polls%20often%20get%20it%20wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701447240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Faq7kpjgc_evm-generic_625x300_21_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmizoram-assembly-election-vote-counting-day-changed-to-december-4-4625357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20revised%20the