he%2C%20his%20work%2C%20and%20his%20writings%20generated%20across%20the%20world%20and%20across%20segments%20of%20opinion.%20From%20academia%20to%20the%20policy%20world%2C%20from%20public%20intellectuals%20to%20diplomats%2C%20from%20journalists%20to%20international%20affairs%20enthusiasts%20-%20everyone%20has%20a%20verdict%20ready%20for%20a%20personality%20that%20towered%20over%20the%20world%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20statecraft%20for%20the%20last%20several%20decades.%20In%20this%20day%20and%20age%20when%20everyone%20has%20an%20opinion%20on%20everything%2C%20pronouncing%20a%20verdict%20on%20Kissinger%20is%20perhaps%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20things%20one%20can%20do.%20And%20we%20are%20relishing%20it%20and%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHenry%20Alfred%20Kissinger%20has%20been%20reviled%20and%20celebrated%20in%20equal%20measure%20but%20there%20can%20be%20no%20denying%20that%20he%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20Western%20diplomats%2C%20who%20shaped%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%20The%20way%20he%20shaped%20it%20has%20continued%20to%20structure%20global%20politics%20to%20date.%20Just%20in%20July%2C%20China%20invited%20the%20centenarian%20to%20open%20a%20line%20of%20communication%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20underlining%20not%20only%20that%20Kissinger%20retained%20an%20unusual%20influence%20on%20world%20politics%2C%20but%20also%20the%20irony%20of%20Beijing%2C%20seemingly%20at%20the%20height%20of%20its%20power%2C%20having%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20diplomat%20who%20had%20left%20office%2046%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20Kissinger's%20impact%20was%20above%20party%20politics.%20His%20views%20were%20sought%20after%20by%20all%20administrations%20and%20he%20had%20the%20ear%20of%20all%20top%20leaders.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20how%20much%20he%20was%20taken%20seriously%20is%20another%20matter%20altogether.%20But%20even%20at%20the%20ripe%20age%20of%20100%2C%20his%20star%20power%20had%20not%20diminished%20and%20he%20retained%20the%20ability%20to%20dazzle%20with%20his%20one-liners%20and%20astute%20observations.%20His%20uncanny%20ability%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20news%20allowed%20him%20a%20larger-than-life%20aura%20that%20he%20sustained%20till%20the%20very%20end.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20last%20public%20appearances%2C%20he%20nonchalantly%20asked%20his%20successors%2C%20Hillary%20Clinton%20and%20James%20Baker%2C%20whom%20they%20considered%20the%20greatest%20secretary%20of%20state%20since%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPower%2C%20for%20Kissinger%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ultimate%20aphrodisiac%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20search%20for%20power%20whether%20for%20himself%20or%20for%20the%20US%20-%20his%20adopted%20country%20-%20led%20him%2C%20at%20times%2C%20in%20directions%20that%20he%20himself%20struggled%20to%20rationalize.%20But%20a%20search%20for%20stability%20and%20order%20devoid%20of%20the%20constraints%20of%20ideology%20or%20morality%20remained%20the%20premise%20around%20which%20he%20had%20built%20his%20own%20diplomatic%20and%20intellectual%20empire.%20As%20he%20argued%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20management%20of%20a%20balance%20of%20power%20is%20a%20permanent%20undertaking%2C%20not%20an%20exertion%20that%20has%20a%20foreseeable%20end%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20this%20management%20saw%20him%20leading%20to%20the%20policy%20of%20d%26amp%3B%23233%3Btente%20with%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20the%20opening%20up%20to%20China%2C%20his%20shuttle%20diplomacy%20resulting%20in%20the%20end%20of%20the%201973%20Arab-Israeli%20conflict%2C%20and%20the%20Paris%20Peace%20Accords%20which%20concluded%20America's%20Vietnam%20misadventure.%20But%20this%20also%20led%20to%20America%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20serious%20human%20rights%20abuses%20by%20various%20military%20regimes%20and%20often%20pandering%20to%20military%20strongmen%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20from%20Chile%20and%20Argentina%20to%20Pakistan.%20For%20many%2C%20Kissinger's%20complicity%20in%20such%20policy%20choices%20made%20him%20perhaps%20the%20world's%20foremost%20war%20criminal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger's%20statecraft%20derived%20from%20his%20realpolitik%20worldview%20may%20at%20times%20seem%20out%20of%20fashion%20but%20it%20continues%20to%20inform%20policy%20choices%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20it%20is%20explicitly%20acknowledged.%20As%20a%20student%20of%20Bismarck%20and%20Metternich%2C%20Kissinger%20was%20categorical%20that%20foreign%20policy%2C%20to%20be%20effective%2C%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bbased%20not%20on%20sentiment%20but%20on%20an%20assessment%20of%20strength.%26quot%3B%20Global%20challenges%20required%20a%20thorough%20engagement%20with%20the%20ever-evolving%20balance%20of%20power%2C%20not%20an%20idealistic%20pursuit%20of%20norms%20in%20a%20void.%20He%20was%20clear%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20country%20that%20demands%20moral%20perfection%20in%20its%20foreign%20policy%20will%20achieve%20neither%20perfection%20nor%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20realism-inspired%20partnership%20of%20Kissinger%20with%20President%20Richard%20Nixon%20that%20according%20to%20George%20C%20Herring%20resulted%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20foreign%20policy%20that%20was%20sometimes%20bold%20and%20imaginative%20in%20conception%2C%20sometimes%20crude%20and%20improvised%2C%20sometimes%20brilliant%20in%20execution%2C%20sometimes%20bungling%3B%20a%20policy%20dedicated%20to%20the%20noble%20goal%20of%20a%20'generation%20of%20peace%2C'%20but%20frequently%20ruthless%20and%20cynical%20in%20the%20use%20of%20military%20power.%26quot%3B%20The%20world%20is%20still%20being%20shaped%20by%20the%20transformative%20changes%20ushered%20in%20the%20global%20order%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger%20recognized%20the%20need%20to%20break%20the%20Sino-Soviet%20alliance%20and%20it%20was%20his%20outreach%20to%20China%20that%20essentially%20changed%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20by%20shifting%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20America's%20favour.%20The%20Cold%20War%20may%20have%20ended%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20but%20it%20was%20Kissinger%20who%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20that%20end%20in%20the%201970s.%20The%20Middle%20East%20of%20today%20also%20owes%20its%20origins%20to%20Kissingerian%20diplomatic%20outreach%20as%20he%20worked%20to%20make%20the%20US%20indispensable%20to%20regional%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Xi%20Jinping%20says%20%26quot%3BChina%20and%20the%20United%20States'%20relations%20will%20forever%20be%20linked%20to%20the%20name%20'Kissinger%2C'%26quot%3B%20and%20when%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Anthony%20Blinken%2C%20while%20travelling%20in%20Israel%2C%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Bfew%20people%20were%20better%20students%20of%20history%20-%20even%20fewer%20people%20did%20more%20to%20shape%20history%20-%20than%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20are%20merely%20stating%20the%20obvious.%20The%20Kissinger%20overhang%20on%20contemporary%20global%20politics%20is%20huge.%20The%20US%20and%20the%20world%20are%20still%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20choices%20America%20made%20under%20Kissinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20perhaps%20his%20last%20public%20remarks%20in%20October%2C%20he%20suggested%20that%20given%20the%20challenges%20of%20today%2C%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bmust%20develop%20a%20concept%20of%20where%20we%20are%20going%20and%20how%20we%20intend%20to%20get%20there%20across%20party%20lines%20and%20through%20political%20differences.%20Such%20is%20the%20requirement%20of%20leadership.%26quot%3B%20It%20may%20sound%20a%20tad%20academic%20but%20Kissinger%20seems%20to%20be%20alluding%20to%20a%20palpable%20lack%20of%20strategy%20in%20American%20foreign-making%20today%20where%20engagement%20with%20long-term%20structural%20trends%20seems%20to%20be%20giving%20way%20to%20ad%20hoc%20tactical%20policy%20prescriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20in%20the%20end%20might%20be%20his%20biggest%20legacy%20-%20using%20diplomacy%20effectively%20to%20achieve%20tangible%20outcomes%20while%20remaining%20alert%20to%20its%20limits%20in%20shaping%20global%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20book%20is%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20Afghan%20Muddle%26quot%3B%20(HarperCollins)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701441900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fs9a9o238_henry-kissinger-afp-_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhenry-kissinger-worldview-and-his-legacy-4625163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20perhaps%20inevitable%20that%20Henry%20Kissinger%20would%20be%20as%20controversial%20in%20his%20death%20as%20he%20was%20during%20his%20life.%20His%20obits%20reflect%20the%20extremities%20of%20passion%20he%2C%20his%20work%2C%20and%20his%20writings%20generated%20across%20the%20world%20and%20across%20segments%20of%20opinion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhenry-kissinger-worldview-and-his-legacy-4625163%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Resort%20Politics%2C%20No%20Poaching%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress'%20DK%20Shivakumar%20After%20Exit%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENo%20Congress%20leader%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bpoached%26quot%3B%2C%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdk-shivakumar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDK%20Shivakumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20NDTV%20Friday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20exit%20polls%20gave%20the%20party%20a%20surprise%20win%20over%20the%20BRS%20in%20the%20Telangana%20Assembly%20election%20and%20an%20outside%20shot%20at%20defeating%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20poll