ches%20opposition%20lawmakers)%20and%20it%20won't%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar%20also%20said%20his%20sources%20had%20told%20him%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%2C%20or%20KCR%2C%20had%20already%20approached%20several%20Congress%20leaders.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20not%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20defeat%20the%20BRS%20that%20has%20ruled%20Telangana%20since%20its%20formation%20in%202014%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ftelangana-election-exit-polls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexit%20polls%20indicate%20it%20will%20get%20at%20least%2062%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20119-member%20Assembly%20and%20the%20BRS%2044.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-exit-polls-kcr-in-trouble-in-telangana-as-congress-gains-ground-suggest-exit-polls-4621560%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKCR%20In%20Trouble%20In%20Telangana%20As%20Congress%20Surges%20Ahead%3A%20NDTV%20Poll%20Of%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20restrained%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20told%20NDTV%20that%20while%20he%2C%20personally%2C%20did%20not%20believe%20exit%20polls%2C%20his%20own%20post-poll%20surveys%20and%20calculations%20have%20pointed%20to%20a%20big%20Congress%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonally%20I%20don't%20believe%20in%20exit%20polls...%20this%20is%20my%20personal%20opinion.%20When%20I%20do%20my%20own%20surveys%20I%20take%20a%20sample%20of%20over%20a%20lakh.%20What%20the%20media%20does%20is%20take%20a%20sample%20size%20of%205%2C000-6%2C000...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20can%20see%2C%20in%20Telangana%20and%20other%20states%2C%20there%20is%20a%20big%20wave.%20People%20want%20change...%20they%20want%20the%20Congress%20to%20come%20to%20power%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20thi