o.%20He%20is%20a%20great%20human%20being%20and%20a%20sound%20leader.%20He%20will%20handle%20it%20with%20grace%20(if%20Pandya%20is%20made%20MI%20leader)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20news%20agency%20PTI%20during%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgXwOS5OS21U%26t%3D126s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20interaction%20with%20former%20cricketer%20S.%20Badrinath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20history%20of%20IPL%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20top%20four%20to%20five%20teams%2C%20all%20have%20released%20players.%20Mumbai%20and%20CSK%20have%20never%20done%20it.%20I%20know%20Hardik%20to%20an%20extent.%20I%20see%20this%20move%20as%20a%20milestone%20achievement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20retirement%20plan%2C%20Ashwin%2C%2037%2C%20said%20the%20day%20he%20loses%20motivation%2C%20he%20would%20call%20it%20quits.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20being%20diplomatic%2C%20but%20for%20four%20to%20five%20years%20(since%202019)%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20in%20a%20very%20dark%20space%20in%20life%2C%20and%20took%20help%20for%20mental%20health%20as%20well.%20In%20the%20dark%20space%2C%20I%20realised%20I%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20any%20eventuality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20preparing%20for%20life%20after%20cricket%20for%20five%20years.%20But%20I%20continue%20to%20work%20hard%20on%20my%20cricket%3B%20to%20contribute%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20USA%20and%20practised%20baseball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20day%20I%20lose%20this%20motivation%2C%20I%20feel%20irritated%20about%20waking%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20bowl%20or%20bat%2C%20I%20know%20it%20is%20over.%20I%20will%20then%20quit%20immediately%2C%20say%20thanks%20to%20all%20and%20go%20on%20to%20the%20next%20chapter%20in%20life.%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20he%20has%20not%20yet%20decided%20on%20his%20post-retireme