%22Cristiano%20Ronaldo%20Faces%20%241%20Billion%20Lawsuit%20Over%20Binance%20Cryptocurrency%20Ads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECristiano%20Ronaldo%20is%20currently%20embroiled%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20involving%20a%20staggering%20%241%20billion%20lawsuit%20for%20his%20endorsement%20of%20Binance%2C%20the%20global%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20district%20court%20in%20Florida%2C%20contends%20that%20the%20former%20Manchester%20United%20and%20Real%20Madrid%20stars%20%26quot%3Bpromoted%2C%20assisted%20in%2C%20and%2For%20actively%20participated%20in%20the%20offer%20and%20sale%20of%20unregistered%20securities%20in%20coordination%20with%20Binance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20claim%20his%20endorsement%20led%20them%20to%20make%20loss-making%20investments.%20They%20are%20seeking%20damages%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20sum%20exceeding%26quot%3B%20%241%20billion%20(Rs%208331%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67566602%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20November%202022%2C%20Binance%20announced%20its%20first%20%26quot%3BCR7%26quot%3B%20collection%20of%20non-fungible%20tokens%20(NFTs)%20in%20partnership%20with%20Ronaldo%2C%20which%20the%20footballer%20said%20would%20reward%20fans%20%26quot%3Bfor%20all%20the%20years%20of%20support.%26quot%3B%20NFTs%20are%20virtual%20assets%20that%20can%20be%20bought%20and%20sold%20but%20have%20no%20real-world%20form%20of%20their%20own%3B%20in%20other%20words%2C%20they%20only%20exist%20digitally.%20Generally%2C%20they%20are%20used%20to%20mark%20ownership%20of%20something%2C%20such%20as%20a%20picture%20or%20video%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCR7%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20Ronaldo's%20initials%20and%20shirt%20number%20and%20is%20used%20as%20branding%20in%20a%20range%20of%20products%2C%20from%20footwear%20to%20fragrances%2C%20that%20have%20helped%20make%20him%20one%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20athletes%20on%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20portal%20further%20said%20that%20the%20claimants%20allege%20that%20Ronaldo's%20promotion%20of%20Binance%20led%20to%20a%20%26quot%3B500%25%20increase%20in%20searches%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20crypto%20exchange%2C%20which%20is%20registered%20in%20the%20Cayman%20Islands.They%20also%20say%20it%20led%20people%20to%20use%20the%20firm%20to%20invest%20in%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3Bunregistered%20securities%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20Binance's%20BNB%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20(SEC)%2C%20these%20assets%20can%20be%20considered%20securities%2C%20and%20so%20celebrities%20endorsing%20them%20must%20follow%20US%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20celebrities%20endorse%20investment%20opportunities%2C%20including%20crypto-asset%20securities%2C%20investors%20should%20be%20careful%20to%20research%20if%20the%20investments%20are%20right%20for%20them%2C%20and%20they%20should%20know%20why%20celebrities%20are%20making%20those%20endorsements%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20chairman%20Gary%20Gensler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701436680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fkt974bqo_cristiano-ronaldo_625x300_24_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcristiano-ronaldo-faces-1-billion-lawsuit-over-binance-cryptocurrency-advertisements-4624946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cristiano%20Ronaldo%2C%20the%20Portuguese%20and%20former%20Manchester%20United%20footballer%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20lawsuit%20seeking%20%26quot%3Ba%20sum%20exceeding%26quot%3B%20%241%20billion%20over%20his%20promotion%20of%20Binance%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20cryptocurrency%20exchange.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcristiano-ronaldo-faces-1-billion-lawsuit-over-bi