rs%20despite%20fears%20over%20its%20silence%20on%20the%20role%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20%26quot%3BThe%20declaration%20doesn't%20set%20out%20how%20governments%20will%20tackle%20food%20emissions%2C%20and%20makes%20no%20reference%20to%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20despite%20food%20systems%20accounting%20for%20at%20least%2015%20percent%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20burned%20each%20year%20--equivalent%20to%20the%20emissions%20of%20all%20EU%20countries%20and%20Russia%20combined%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fover-130-nations-agree-to-include-food-agriculture-in-climate-plans%2Farticleshow%2F105660346.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fover-130-nations-agree-to-include-food-agriculture-in-climate-plans%2Famp_articleshow%2F105660346.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fover-130-nations-agree-to-include-food-agriculture-in-climate-plans%2Famp_articleshow%2F105660346.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Cop%20In%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20Security%20Detail%20vs%203-Time%20Chief%20Minister%20In%20Mizoram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20tight%20electoral%20contest%20in%20Mizoram%20boils%20down%20to%20two%20men%20with%20completely%20different%20backgrounds.%20One%20was%20the%20leader%20of%20an%20insurgent%20group.%20The%20other%20was%20a%20police%20officer%20who%20served%20as%20the%20security%20in-charge%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20Lalduhoma%2C%2074%2C%20founded%20the%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20by%20merging%20six%20parties%20to%20take%20on%20Zoramthanga%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20was%20a%20guerilla%20fighting%20the%20Indian%20military%20before%20joining%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-clear-winner-in-mizoram-hung-assembly-likely-predict-2-exit-polls-4621718%5C%22%3ENDTV%20poll%20of%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20showed%20the%20ZPM%20getting%20at%20least%2017%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%2040-member%20Mizoram%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga's%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20is%20projected%20to%20get%2014%20seats%2C%20according%20to%20NDTV's%20poll%20of%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20indicated%20there%20would%20be%20no%20clear%20winner%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20assembly%20election.%20Initial%20exit%20polls%20by%20Jan%20Ki%20Baat%20showed%20the%20ZPM%20may%20win%20at%20least%20anywhere%20between%2015%20and%2025%20seats%20in%20the%2040-member%20assembly%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20MNF%20with%2010%20to%2014%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ZPM%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalduhoma%20was%20the%20first%20MP%20to%20be%20disqualified%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20under%20an%20anti-defection%20law%20in%201988%2C%20and%20later%20also%20became%20the%20first%20MLA%20to%20be%20disqualified%20from%20the%20Mizoram%20assembly%20in%20November%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wore%20several%20shoes%20during%20his%20police%20career%2C%20including%20serving%20as%20the%20security%20in-charge%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201982.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ZPM%20has%20promised%20the%20people%20of%20Mizoram%20a%20%26quot%3Bmuch-needed%26quot%3B%20change%20from%20Zoramthanga's%20policies%2C%20which%20the%20ZPM%20alleged%20have%20led%20to%20a%20slowdown%20in%20the%20development%20of%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20ZPM%20are%20getting%20closer%20and%20keeping%20options%20open%20for%20an%20alliance%20if%20the%20need%20arises%20due%20to%20a%20hung%20assembly.%20The%20ZPM%20emerged%20as%20the%20second-largest%20party%20in%20Mizoram%20in%20the%20last%20election%20after%20winning%20eight%20seats%20in%20the%2040-member%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZoramthanga%20Gives%20A%20Fight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga%2C%2079%2C%20is%20a%20three-time%20Chief%20Minister.%20He%20has%20not%20only%20sheltered%20thousands%20of%20internally%20displaced%20Kuki%20tribes%20from%20Manipur%20and%20Myanmar%2C%20but%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20stand%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Manipur%20led%20by%20his%20counterpart%20N%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20MNF%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20Zoramthanga%20-%20citing%20kinship%20and%20familial%20ties%20with%20the%20Chin-Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Myanmar%20-%20has%20openly%20given%20shelter%20to%20at%20least%2040%2C000%20refugees%20who%20fled%20from%20the%20junta%20rule%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga%20has%20been%20a%20veteran%20of%20many%20elections%3B%20some%20he%20won%2C%20some%20he%20lost.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20tough%20four-way%20electoral%20battle%20with%20many%20parties%20in%20the%20arena.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20however%2C%20is%20optimistic%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20will%20help%20his%20party%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20Laldenga%2C%20who%20waged%20a%20two-decade-long%20guerilla%20war%20against%20India%20for%20independence%20for%20a%20sovereign%20Mizo%20nation%20until%20the%20signing%20of%20a%20peace%20agreement%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga%20became%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20MNF%20after%20Laldenga%20died%20in%201990%3B%20the%20party%20lost%20the%201993%20assembly%20election%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20Zoramthanga%20won%20from%20Champhai%20seat%20and%20became%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoramthanga%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201998%20after%20the%20MNF%20won%20the%20state%20election.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20MNF%20have%20been%20in%20power%20on%20and%20off%20in%