nded%20and%20casualties%20were%20reported%20in%20the%20first%20few%20minutes%20after%20the%20fighting%20resumed.%20Israel%20vowed%20to%20uproot%20Hamas%20after%20the%20deadly%20October%207%20attack%20in%20which%201%2C400%20were%20killed.%20Over%2014%2C000%20have%20died%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20all-out%20ground%20and%20air%20assault%20in%20Gaza%20has%20brought%20the%20use%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20back%20into%20focus.%20In%202021%2C%20Israel%20launched%20'Operation%20Guardians%20of%20the%20Wall'%20in%20its%20offensive%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%20The%2011-day%20fighting%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20'First%20AI%20war'.%20The%20data%20gathered%20from%20AI%20tools%20were%20used%20to%20strike%20targets%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BGospel%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BAlchemist%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Depth%20of%20Wisdom%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20war%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20is%20employing%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20targets%20and%20conducting%20precision%20air%20strikes%20in%20Gaza.%20Systems%20like%20%26quot%3BGospel%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BAlchemist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDepth%20of%20Wisdom%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20were%20used%20before%20are%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESystems%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BGospel%26quot%3B%20are%20being%20used%20to%20allow%20automatic%20tools%20to%20produce%20targets%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%2C%20and%20works%20by%20improving%20accurate%20and%20high-quality%20intelligence%20material%20according%20to%20the%20requirement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20help%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20through%20the%20rapid%20and%20automatic%20extraction%20of%20updated%20intelligence%20-%20it%20produces%20a%20recommendation%20for%20the%20researcher%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20being%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20complete%20match%20between%20the%20machine's%20recommendation%20and%20the%20identification%20performed%20by%20a%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IDF%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Farab-israeli-conflict%2Fgaza-news%2Fguardian-of-the-walls-the-first-ai-war-669371%5C%22%3EIn%20the%202021%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20data%20from%20Human%20Intelligence%20(HUMINT)%2C%20Visual%20Intelligence%20(VISINT)%20and%20Signal%20Intelligence%20(SIGINT)%20are%20collected%20and%20fed%20into%20systems%20to%20help%20create%20data%20to%20conduct%20precision%20strikes.%20The%20data%20from%20satellites%2C%20ground%20intelligence%20and%20surveillance%20are%20all%20crunched%20into%20these%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMass%20Assasination%20Factory%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%2C%20in%20its%20article%20dated%20November%202%2C%20claimed%20that%20over%2012%2C000%20targets%20have%20been%20hit%20in%2027%20days%20of%20fighting%2C%20i.e.%2C%20almost%20444%20targets%20a%20day.%20The%20increase%20in%20targets%20is%20due%20to%20data%20generated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGospel%26quot%3B%20can%20generate%20targets%20at%20an%20automatic%20rate%20and%20exceeds%20what%20was%20previously%20possible%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fmass-assassination-factory-israel-calculated-bombing-gaza%2F%5C%22%3E%2B972%20Mag%20and%20Local%20Call%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20adding%2C%20that%20this%20AI%20system%2C%20as%20described%20by%20a%20former%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20essentially%20facilitates%20a%20%26quot%3Bmass%20assassination%20factory%26quot%3B.%20The%20recommendations%20are%20used%20to%20incorporate%20AI-based%20platforms%20like%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20platforms%20crunch%20data%20to%20select%20targets%20for%20air%20strikes.%20Ensuing%20raids%20can%20then%20be%20rapidly%20assembled%20with%20another%20artificial%20intelligence%20model%20called%20Fire%20Factory%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-16%2Fisrael-using-ai-systems-to-plan-deadly-military-operations%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Fire%20Factory%20calculates%20munition%20loads%2C%20prioritizes%20and%20assigns%20thousands%20of%20targets%20to%20aircraft%20and%20drones%2C%20and%20proposes%20a%20schedule%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20processed%20by%20an%20AI%20tool%20like%20Gospel%20was%20used%20by%20the%20IDF%20to%20select%20targets%20to%20be%20hit%20in%20Hamas%2C%20this%20includes%20Hamas%20operatives%20that%20have%20to%20be%20assassinated.%20The%20target%20division%20has%20helped%20the%20IDF%20build%20a%20database%20of%20what%20sources%20said%20was%20between%2030%2C000%20and%2040%2C000%20suspected%20militants%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fdec%2F01%2Fthe-gospel-how-israel-uses-ai-to-select-bombing-targets%5C%22%3Ethe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAviv%20Kochavi%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20IDF%20until%20January%2C%20has%20said%20the%20target%20division%20is%20%26quot%3Bpowered%20by%20AI%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20and%20includes%20hundreds%20of%20officers%20and%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Israel%20Aerospace%20Industries%20and%20Matrix%20Defense%20partnered%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20to%20develop%20automated-%20target%20detection%20systems.%20The%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defense%20Systems%20has%20incorporated%20AI%20into%20Spice%20Bombs%20and%20other%20technologies%20used%20for%20surveillance.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701435060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ff5vac938_israel-gaza-violence_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-over-14-000-dead-in-gaza-how-israel-is-using-ai-to-conduct-air-strikes-4624859%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%20re