%2C%20and%20would%2C%20remain%20an%20important%20part%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20energy%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kwatra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fcoal-will-remain-an-important-part-of-indias-energy-needs-govt-official-11833921.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%20ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20trip%20to%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20relies%20on%20coal%20for%2073%25%20of%20its%20energy%20needs.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20another%2017%20gigawatts%20of%20power%20from%20coal-based%20power%20plants%20to%20fulfill%20its%20rising%20energy%20demands.%20This%20particular%20addition%20is%20the%20fastest%20in%20recent%20times.%20India%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20from%20major%20powers%20of%20the%20world%20for%20allegedly%20not%20being%20able%20to%20reduce%20its%20reliance%20on%20coal-based%20energy%20fast%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20along%20with%20China%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20oppose%20any%20discussion%20or%20decision%20that%20were%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20conference%20which%20could%20potentially%20put%20strictures%20on%20coal-fired%20power%20stations.%20France%20and%20the%20United%20States%20are%20expected%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20on%20private%20financing%20of%20these%20plants%20at%20the%20COP28%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKwatra%20said%20India%20is%20among%C2%A0a%20handful%20of%20large%20economies%20that%20are%20on%20track%20to%20fulfil%20all%20their%20climate%20commitments.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20major%20economies%20that%20is%20well%20on%20track%20to%20complete%20its%20obligated%20NDCs%20(Nationally%20Determined%20Contributions).%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20had%20announced%20and%20upgraded%20our%20NDCs%20last%20year%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20happy%20to%20say%20that%20we%20are%20now%20well%20on%20our%20way%20even%20to%20meet%20those%20upgraded%20NDC%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%