er%20and%20was%20reported%20missing%20on%20November%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Metropolitan%20Police%20discovered%20his%20body%20in%20the%20river%20Thames%20near%20the%20Canary%20Wharf%20area%20of%20east%20London%20on%20November%2021%20and%20was%20declared%20dead%20by%20paramedics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20death%20is%20not%20believed%20to%20be%20suspicious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Met%20Police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParth%20Patel%2C%20a%20relative%2C%20has%20since%20launched%20a%20Go%20Fund%20Me%20online%20fundraiser%20and%20raised%20over%20GBP%204%2C500%20since%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMitkumar%20Patel%20was%20a%2023-year%20(old)%20boy%20who%20came%20to%20the%20UK%20for%20higher%20studies%20on%2019th%20September%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20fundraising%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20belonged%20to%20a%20farmer%20family%20and%20used%20to%20live%20in%20a%20village%20as%20well.%20He%20was%20missing%20from%20November%2017%2C%202023.%20Now%20on%20November%2021%20police%20found%20his%20dead%20body%20from%20Canary%20Wharf%20in%20the%20water.%20It%20was%20sad%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20fund%20raising%20for%20helping%20out%20his%20family%20and%20to%20send%20his%20body%20to%20India%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20reiterates%20that%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20safely%20transmitted%20to%20Mitkumar's%20family%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20'Evening%20Standard'%20newspaper%2C%20the%20student%20was%20due%20to%20move%20to%20Sheffield%20on%20November%2020%20to%20start%20a%20degree%20at%20Sheffield%20Hallam%20University%20and%20a%20part-time%20job%20at%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20failed%20to%20return%20from%20a%20daily%20walk%20to%20the%20home%20where%20he%20was%20staying%20in%20London%2C%20his%20relatives%20grew%20worried%20and%20reported%20him%20missing.%20They%20later%20found%20that%20he%20had%20left%20his%20set%2