%20only%20implying%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan%2Fpanauti-modi-rahul-gandhi-takes-dig-at-pm-for-indias-world-cup-debacle-2779356%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epanauti%20in%20Ahmedabad%20had%20caused%20India%20to%20lose%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Australia%2C%20but%20later%20went%20full%20frontal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20word%20has%20stuck%2C%20picking%20up%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSirKazamJeevi%2Fstatus%2F1729468597418815928%3Ft%3DPvEM0Lb5CUrhukImNvlHPw%26s%3D03%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etraction%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewhere%20all%20kinds%20of%20jokes%20and%20references%20are%20being%20made%20using%20it.%20The%20BJP%20understands%20that%2C%20hence%20the%20objection.%20So%20far%20the%20EC%20has%20not%20taken%20action%20against%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20in%20getting%20hot%20and%20bothered%20about%20it%2C%20the%20BJP%20protests%20too%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20recently%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20talked%20about%20how%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20family%20were%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShahOffice%2Fstatus%2F1727558768265949517%5C%22%3ERahu%20Ketu%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20(bad%20omens)%20of%20India%2C%20a%20statement%20that%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20office%20had%20proudly%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Modi%20himself%20had%20called%20his%20Congress%20rival%20as%20%3Cem%3Emoorkhon%20ka%20sardar%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(the%20chief%20of%20fools).%20To%20then%20raise%20a%20hue%20and%20cry%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20seems%20churlish.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20BJP%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20agitated%20response%20against%20Gandhi%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20background%20of%20a%20changing%20political%20environment%2C%20when%20he%20and%20his%20party%20are%20doing%20well%20and%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fexit-polls-assembly-elections-2023-november-bjp-congress-brs%5C%22%3Elikely%20to%20put%20up%20a%20good%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20whose%20results%20will%20be%20known%20on%20Sunday.%20Predicting%20election%20results%20is%20always%20hazardous%2C%20but%20if%20the%20Congress%20wins%20in%20two%20or%20three%20of%20them%2C%20or%20at%20least%20comes%20out%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20big%20boost%20after%20the%20handsome%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20recently.%20This%20will%20put%20it%20in%20pole%20position%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20will%20then%20confidently%20face%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20Modi%20is%20not%20the%20charmed%20leader%20that%20he%20was%20seven%20or%20eight%20years%20ago%20when%20he%20could%20do%20no%20wrong.%20The%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20conflict%20with%20China%2C%20in%20which%20India%20has%20lost%20territory%20and%20even%20the%20inability%20to%20speak%20on%20many%20domestic%20issues%20have%20shown%20a%20lack%20of%20leadership.%20The%20impression%20that%20he%20is%20very%20close%20to%20billionaire%20capitalists%2C%20especially%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20is%20now%20well%20entrenched.%20The%20last%20time%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20hit%20home%20was%20when%20he%20called%20the%20Modi%20government%20a%20%3Cem%3Esuit-boot%20ki%20sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202015%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20government%20giving%20up%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fsuit-boot-sarkar-repeat-could-sharpen-bjps-hindutva-turn-in-up-1052343.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econtroversial%20land%20Bill%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20soon%20after%20and%20instead%20introducing%20social%20welfare%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20Modi%20government%20or%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20politically%20fear%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20It%20had%20won%20the%202014%20elections%20handsomely%20and%20the%20Congress%20had%20been%20reduced%20to%2044%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20called%20%3Cem%3EPappu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Post-2014%2C%20that%20was%20the%20nickname%20given%20to%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20and%20the%20meaning%20was%20clear%E2%80%94he%20was%20an%20ignoramus%2C%20a%20babe%20in%20the%20political%20woods%2C%20a%20clueless%20dynast%20who%20was%20no%20threat%20to%20anyone%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20giant%20BJP%20machine.%20He%20may%20make%20the%20occasional%20noise%2C%20but%20that%20would%20not%20translate%20into%20votes%20or%20seats%20and%20could%20be%20safely%20ignored.%20An%20entire%20industry%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20to%20ridicule%20him%2C%20composed%20mainly%20of%20the%20right-wing%20ecosystem.%20Joining%20them%20were%20the%20neutrals%2C%20the%20fence-sitting%20commentators%20who%20made%20fun%20of%20him%20and%20his%20attempts%20to%20be%20a%20politician%20%E2%80%93%20why%20does%20he%20travel%20so%20much%2C%20they%20asked%2C%20is%20he%20even%20serious%3F%20They%20even%20made%20fun%20of%20his%20on-off%20beard%20%E2%80%93%20make%20up%20your%20mind%2C%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20knew%20this%2C%20and%20once%20in%20Parliament%20referenced%20the%20name%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20admitting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-confidence-motion-you-may-call-me-pappu-i-dont-hate-you-rahul-gandhi-hugs-pm-modi-1886780%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20knew%20he%20was%20called%20Pappu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20then%20walked%20across%20and%20embraced%20Modi%20in%20a%20bear%20hug.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20any%20difference%20politically%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%202019%20elections%20with%20an%20even%20bigger%20majority%2C%20but%20in%20retrospect%20showed%20that%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20going%20to%20disappear%20from%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20big%20moment%20came%20when%20he%20undertook%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20a%20long%20walk%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20people%20joining%20him%20at%20various%20points.%20He%20met%20the%20press%2C%20spoke%20with%20citizens%20along%20the%20way%2C%20and%20displayed%20resilience%20and%20determination%3B%20the%20mainstream%20media%20gave%20him%20minimal%20coverage%2C%20but%20social%20media%20and%20the%20international%20press%20amplified%20it.%20It%20provided%20a%20contrast%20with%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20all%20about%20self-aggrandisation.%20Whether%20going%20off%20to%20international%20summits%20or%20exploiting%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20presidency%20%E2%80%93%20a%20rotational%20affair%20for%20member%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20not%20found%20time%20to%20devote%20to%20critical%20matters%20at%20home%2C%20except%20whenever%20there%20is%20an%20election%20campaign%20or%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20Hindu%20ceremony%20is%20involved.%20Which%20has%20meant%20that%20many%20domestic%20crises%2C%20such%20as%20Manipur%20have%20gone%20unattended.%20Not%20that%20internationally%20things%20are%20any%20better%20%E2%80%93%20even%20with%20friendly%20nations%20near%20and%20far%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20Maldives%20to%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%2C%20our%20relations%20are%20under%20strain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20post-Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20the%20sobriquet%20of%20pappu%20has%20dissipated%20and%20instead%2C%20Gandhi%20is%20perceived%20as%20a%20mature%20political%20leader.%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20is%20now%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20runs%20the%20party.%20In%20most%20states%20going%20to%20elections%2C%20Kharge%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20local%20leadership%2C%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20deferring%20to%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20still%20relies%20on%20its%20biggest%20star%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20work%20in%20West%20Bengal%20or%20Karnataka.%20If%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20may%20not%20%E2%80%93%20the%20same%20happens%20in%20key%20Hindi%20belt%20states%2C%20then%20his%20sheen%20would%20seem%20to%20be%20fading.%20And%20the%20BJP%20has%20no%20second%20line%20of%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20general%20elections%20just%20about%20six%20months%20away%2C%20neither%20Modi%20nor%20the%20BJP%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20seen%20falling%20behind%20and%20not%20just%20electorally.%20It%20is%20a%20short%20period%20in%20which%20he%20will%20want%20to%20show%20he%20continues%20to%20be%20not%20just%20a%20vote%20winner%20but%20also%20capable%20of%20big%2C%20winning%20ideas%20who%20can%20deal%20with%20crises%20on%20the%20domestic%20and%20international%20front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20one%20gives%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20a%20realistic%20chance%20of%20defeating%20a%20Modi-led%20BJP%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20but%20he%20also%20has%20to%20win%20big%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20victory%20he%20and%20his%20party%20have%20got%20used%20to.%20His%20performance%20at%20the%20state%20level%20has%20not%20been%20that%20impressive%2C%20the%20party%20outright%20winning%20only%20in%20two%20big%20states%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20UP%2C%20but%20he%20has%20ensured%20he%20is%20never%20blamed.%20That%20will%20not%20any%20longer%20work%20now%2C%20post%20Karnataka%3B%20the%20party%20has%20to%20post%20not%20just%20one%20but%20two%2C%20maybe%20three%20impressive%20victories%20in%20the%20state%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20if%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20happen%2C%20doubts%20will%20set%20in.%20You%20can%20be%20sure%20then%20that%20the%20opposition%20will%20fully%20exploit%20the%20panauti%20tag.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701430507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F15183239%2FUntitled-design-7.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpappu-panauti-rahul-gandhi-narendra-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20agitated%20response%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20used%20the%20word%20'panauti'%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20background%20of%20a%20changing%20political%20environment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpappu-panauti-rahul-gandhi-narendra-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Report%20in%20SC%20on%20Manipur%20Victims'%20Bodies%20in%20Morgues%20Highlights%20Deep%20Divides%2C%20State%20of%20Law%20and%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20162818%2Fimphal-long-shot-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ordered%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20bury%20the%20unidentified%20and%20unclaimed%20bodies%20of%20individuals%20killed%20during%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20which%20began%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sharp%20divide%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20is%20yet%20to%20abate%20and%20the%20state%20is%20virtually%20split%2C%20with%20the%20Meitei%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%2C%20and%20tribal%20communities%20being%20confined%20to%20the%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20information%20provided%20by%20the%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal%20(retired)%20committee%20to%20the%20top%20court%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20total%20of%20175%20deaths%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%20number%20of%20deaths%20reported%20confirmed%2C%20169%20people%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20have%20been%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighty-one%20bodies%20have%20been%20claimed%20by%20the%20next%20of%20kin%2C%20and%2088%20have%20been%20identified%20by%20the%20administration%20but%20have%20not%20been%20claimed%20yet.%20Six%20bodies%20remain%20unidentified%20(five%20in%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20one%20in%20the%20Regional%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences).%20For%20these%20six%20unidentified%20bodies%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Students%E2%80%99%20Organisation%2C%20D.J.%20Haokip%2C%20underlined%20the%20precarious%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20divide%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20enter%20Imphal.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20have%20said%20what%20I%20told%20you%20before%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20verify%20all%20the%20bodies%20with%20all%20their%20relevant%20documents%2C%20but%20the%20government%20has%20to%20provide%20us%20security%20to%20enter%20Imphal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsg-tushar-mehtas-claim-that-unclaimed-bodies-in-manipur-belong-to-infiltrators-is-unfounded%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20of%20the%20bodies%20in%20morgues%20in%20Manipur%20are%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D.%20His%20claims%20were%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20facts.%20Even%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20been%20able%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20confirm%20only%2019%20bodies%20were%20unidentified%20in%20Manipur.%20However%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20even%20identified%20bodies%20remained%20in%20hospital%20morgues%20as%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20were%20being%20unable%20to%20travel%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20by%20the%20committee%20includes%20bodies%20of%20victims%20from%20both%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities.%20Most%20victims%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20are%20in%20JNIMS%20and%20RIMS%20Hospital%20in%20Imphal%2C%20while%20Meitei%20bodies%20are%20in%20Churachandpur%20district.%20This%20again%20underscores%20how%20the%20state%20is%20divided%20between%20the%20ethnic%20groups%2C%20with%20no%20visible%20effort%20being%20made%20by%20the%20state%20to%20enable%20peaceful%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%2C%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20154%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20This%20number%20includes%20missing%20persons%20too.%20ITLF%20data%20also%20states%20that%20there%20are%2022%20people%20from%20the%20community%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20their%20bodies%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20arises%3A%20how%20were%20these%20bodies%20identified%20when%20Meiteis%20can%E2%80%99t%20enter%20the%20hills%20and%20Kukis%20can%E2%80%99t%20enter%20the%20valley%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20kin%20of%20the%20deceased%20whose%20body%20is%20in%20the%20Imphal%20morgue.%20Nenghoikim%20Lhungdim%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20brother%20Jamkholal%20Lhungdim%20and%20her%20sister-in-law%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Ngamkhothang%20Lhungdim%20were%20killed%20in%20Imphal.%20Nenghoikim%20remembers%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20May%204%20morning%2C%20all%20the%20people%20in%20Khongsai%20Veng%20were%20asked%20to%20stay%20together%20in%20Lodestar%20Public%20School.%20Later%2C%20when%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20were%20moving%20out%2C%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20with%20iron%20rods%20and%20killed.%E2%80%9D%20Their%20bodies%20are%20lying%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20RIMS%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20her%20family%20identified%20their%20late%20kin%E2%80%99s%20body%20in%20the%20Imphal%20morgue%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20contacted%20the%20police%20and%20got%20photographs%20from%20them%20to%20verify%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EITLF%20spokesperson%20Vualzong%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20go%20to%20Imphal%2C%20but%20the%20district%20administration%20arranges%20photos%20for%20the%20identification%20of%20the%20person.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Nine%20cremation%20sites%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mittal%20committee%20report%20also%20talks%20about%20nine%20cremation%20sites%2C%20The%20Government%20of%20Manipur%20has%20identified%20nine%20sites%20where%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20can%20perform%20last%20rites%20and%20bury%20their%20loved%20ones.%20But%20where%20are%20these%20nine%20sites%3F%20Are%20these%20sites%20on%20the%20hillside%20or%20in%20the%20valley%3F%20The%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20declare%20where%20these%20sites%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20both%20communities%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20about%20these%20%E2%80%9Cnine%20sites%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20Colin%20Gonsalves%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20a%20Kuki%20group%20in%20the%20court.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Gonsalves%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20date%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20these%20nine%20places%20are.%20The%20threat%20is%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20in%20the%20bodies%2C%20the%20government%20will%20bury%20them%20for%20us.%20It%20is%20a%20shocking%20proposition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribal%20community%20is%20aggrieved%20by%20how%20the%20issue%20of%20burial%20has%20been%20handled%20by%20all%20parties.%20They%20have%20been%20desperate%20to%20retrieve%20their%20loved%20ones%E2%80%99%20bodies%20for%20seven%20months.%20Since%20May%2C%20the%20government%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdominant%20community%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20claim%2C%20have%20put%20up%20every%20possible%20obstruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGonsalves%20also%20spoke%20about%20Kuki%20customs%2C%20which%20say%20that%20when%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20are%20killed%20in%20action%2C%20the%20deceased%20members%20are%20buried%20side%20by%20side.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20years%20ago%2C%20during%20an%20agitation%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20when%20seven%C2%A0%20Kukis%20were%20killed%2C%20all%20the%20seven%20Kukis%20were%20buried%20side%20by%20side.%20It%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20tradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20now%2C%20when%20representatives%20of%20the%20tribals%20have%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20home%20ministry%20and%20cleared%20everything%2C%20certain%20individuals%20have%20obstructed%20the%20process.%20And%20what%20is%20the%20threat%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20missing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20a%20total%20of%20175%20people%20died%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20but%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20include%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20that%20happened%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20medical%20facilities.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20that%2045%20people%20have%20already%20died%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-months-later-has-amit-shah-fulfilled-the-promises-he-made-on-manipur%5C%22%3Emedicines%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompensation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEx-Gratia%20payment%20has%20been%20completed%20to%20Noks%20for%2073%20cases%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%20169%20identified%20cases.%20Out%20of%20the%20remaining%2096%20cases%2C%2038%20families%20have%20expressed%20unwillingness%20to%20receive%20the%20assistance%20due%20to%20pressure%20from%20Civil%20Society%20Organizations%20(CSOs)%20like%20ITLF%2C%20JPO%2C%20KIM%2C%20etc.%20For%20the%20remaining%2058%20cases%2C%20verification%20is%20underway%20and%20assistance%20would%20be%20released%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fto-keep-pot-boiling-supreme-court-slams-manipur-groups-over-delaying-burial-cremation-of-unclaimed-bodies-4615781%5C%22%3Ealso%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Cpressure%E2%80%9D%20from%20civil%20society%20organisations%20on%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20to%20not%20perform%20last%20rites.%20This%20allegation%20has%20been%20a%20point%20of%20contention%2C%20with%20civil%20society%20organisations%20often%20being%20the%20sole%20support%20for%20bereaved%20families%20and%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701430249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20162818%2Fimphal-long-shot-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Freport-in-sc-on-manipur-victims-bodies-in-morgues-highlights-deep-divides-state-of-law-and-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Of%20175%20dead%20in%20violence%20raging%20for%20nearly%20eight%20months%20now%2C%20six%20bodies%20lie%20unable%20to%20be%20buried%20or%20cremated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Freport-in-sc-on-manipur-victims-bodies-in-morgues-highlights-deep-divides-state-of-law-and-order%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nick%20Kyrgios%20thanks%20Andy%20Murray%20for%20helpi