the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20success%20in%202024.%20The%20BCCI%20has%20extended%20the%20contract%20of%20India%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20at%20least%20till%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20even%20though%20the%20exact%20duration%20of%20his%20second%20term%20is%20not%20yet%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20Ganguly's%20BCCI%20tenure%20that%20Dravid%20had%20become%20the%20head%20coach%20and%20the%20former%20India%20lefthander%20was%20happy%20for%20his%20teammate's%20contract%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20surprised%20that%20they%20have%20shown%20faith%20in%20Dravid.%20When%20I%20was%20president%20of%20the%20Board%2C%20we%20convinced%20him%20to%20do%20this%20job.%20And%20I'm%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20yesterday%20that%20his%20tenure%20has%20been%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20always%20the%20case%2C%20depending%20on%20whether%20he%20wanted%20it%20or%20not.%20I%20wish%20him%20luck%20for%20another%20World%20Cup%20in%20June.%20He%20was%20very%20close%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20may%20not%20have%20won%20it%2C%20but%20they%20probably%20were%20the%20best%20team%20in%20the%20competition%20with%20the%20way%20they%20played.%20So%20he's%20got%20another%20seven%20months%20for%20a%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%20Hopefully%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20he%20will%20not%20be%20runners-up%2C%20but%20a%20champion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20India's%20title%20drought%20at%20an%20ICC%20global%20showpiece%2C%20Ganguly%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHopefully%20they%20will%20cross%20the%20bridge%20one%20day.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20captain%2C%20I've%20qualified%20for%20three%20finals%2C%20and%20lost%20twice%20--%202003%20World%20Cup%20and%202001%20Champions%20Trophy.%20So%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20right%20to%20say%20how%20to%20win%20finals.%20I%20managed%20just%20one%20win%20that%20too%20as%20joint%20winners%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20(2002%20Champions%20Trophy)%2C%26quot