%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmid%20Scobie's%20'Endgame%3A%20Inside%20the%20Royal%20Family%20and%20the%20Monarchy's%20Fight%20for%20Survival'%20hit%20bookshelves%20around%20the%20world%20this%20week%20and%20repeated%20an%20allegation%20that%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20British%20royal%20family%20had%20raised%20questions%20around%20the%20skin%20colour%20of%20Prince%20Archie%20-%20the%20son%20of%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20Markle%20born%20in%20May%202019.%20Meghan%2C%20of%20African%20American%20heritage%2C%20first%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20an%20unnamed%20royal%20referencing%20their%20first-born's%20skin%20colour%20during%20the%20couple's%20infamous%20interview%20with%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20over%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20main%20edition%20of%20Scobie's%20new%20book%20chose%20not%20to%20name%20the%20senior%20royals%2C%20the%20Dutch%20edition%20included%20the%20allegation%20that%20it%20was%20King%20Charles%20and%20Kate%20who%20had%20discussed%20the%20skin%20colour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20exploring%20all%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20palace%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20most%20UK%20media%20outlets%20were%20holding%20off%20naming%20the%20royals%20but%20it%20has%20been%20dominating%20headlines%20after%20TalkTV%20aired%20the%20names%20of%20Charles%20and%20Kate%20from%20the%20Dutch%20book%20fiasco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20individual%20has%20written%20some%20rumour%20and%20scuttlebutt%20that%20has%20made%20various%20claims%20about%20His%20Majesty%20the%20King%20that%20are%2C%20frankly%2C%20completely%20unproven%2C%26quot%3B%20UK%20Security%20Minister%20Tom%20Tugendhat%20told%20TalkTV%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20King's%20done%20a%20brilliant%20job%20for%20us%2C%20not%20just%20in%20the%20last%20year%20since%20he's%20been%20King%2C%20but%20he's%20been%20absolutely%20fantastic%20for%20many%2C%20many%20years%20in%20arguing%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20British%20people%20as%20Prince%20of%20Wales.%20So%20frankly%20I%20see%20this%20as%20just%20rumour%2C%20hearsay%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20disparage%20somebody%20who's%20served%20our%20country%20with%20enormous%20dignity%20and%20enormous%20grace%20for%20many%2C%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dutch%20publisher%20of%20the%20new%20book%2C%20Xander%20Uitgevers%2C%20said%20it%20had%20been%20pulled%20from%20shelves%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20due%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Berror%26quot%3B.%20Scobie%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20been%20insisting%20it%20was%20not%20part%20of%20some%20publicity%20stunt%20and%20lamented%20that%20the%20row%20had%20%26quot%3Bovershadowed%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20of%20his%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20this%20is%20frustrating%20because%20it%20feeds%20into%20something%20that%20couldn't%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%20And%20also%2C%20quite%20frankly%2C%20I've%20always%20felt%20the%20names%20weren't%20needed%20to%20have%20this%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writer%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20co-authored%20another%20book%20on%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20entitled%20'Finding%20Freedom'%2C%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20cheerleader%20of%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20ever%20since%20they%20stepped%20back%20from%20frontline%20royalty%20back%20in%202020%20and%20relocated%20to%20California.%20He%20has%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20or%20interview%20the%20couple%20for%20the%20latest%20book.%20Representatives%20of%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20have%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20book's%20release%20or%20the%20ensuing%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20interview%20in%20March%202021%2C%20Meghan%20told%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20that%20Harry%20had%20been%20asked%20by%20an%20unnamed%20family%20member%20%26quot%3Bhow%20dark%26quot%3B%20their%20son%20Archie's%20skin%20might%20be.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Bucking