o%20Read%20%7C%20What%20Is%20White%20Lung%20Syndrome%3F%20A%20Mysterious%20Pneumonia%20Outbreak%2C%20Similar%20To%20China's%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disease%20is%20transmitted%20via%20coughing%2C%20sneezing%2C%20talking%2C%20singing%2C%20and%20breathing%2C%20carried%20by%20minuscule%20respiratory%20droplets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20regions%20in%20Ohio%20have%20also%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20enigmatic%20outbreak%2C%20marking%20it%20as%20the%20initial%20location%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20document%20cases%20of%20the%20illness%2C%20particularly%20with%20a%20notably%20elevated%20rate%20of%20children%20requiring%20hospitalization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-news%2Farticles%2F2023-11-30%2Fcdc-director-spike-in-respiratory-illness-in-china-not-from-a-new-virus%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CWhat%2520we%2520do%2520know%2520as%2Cthey%2520are%2520seeing%2520an%2520upsurgence.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUS%20News%20%26amp%3B%20World%20Report%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20announced%20that%20they%20have%20been%20in%20communication%20with%20China%20and%20indicated%20that%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20in%20the%20country%20is%20not%20attributed%20to%20a%20novel%20pathogen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20know%20as%20of%20right%20now%2C%20today%2C%20what's%20happening%20in%20China%20is%20that%20they%20are%20seeing%20an%20increase%20in%20some%20of%20their%20respiratory%20illnesses%3B%20they're%20seeing%20them%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20their%20country%3B%20they're%20seeing%20an%20uptick%20in%20their%20pediatric%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20CDC%20Director%20Mandy%20Cohen%20told%20a%20House%20subcommittee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20do%20know%20as%20of%2C%20again%2C%20as%20of%20today%2C%20is%20that%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20this%20is%20a%20new%20or%20novel%20pathogen.%20We%20believe%20this%20is%20all%20existing%2C%20meaning%20COVID%2C%20flu%2C%20RSV%2C%20and%20mycoplasma.%20But%20they%20are%20seeing%20an%20upsurgence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20White%20Lung%20Syndrome%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20Lung%20Syndrome%20is%20a%20severe%20form%20of%20pneumonia%20that%20can%20cause%20lung%20scarring%20and%20discoloration.%20The%20exact%20cause%20of%20the%20illness%20is%20still%20unknown%2C%20but%20it%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20caused%20by%20a%20combination%20of%20bacterial%2C%20viral%2C%20and%20environmental%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESymptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESymptoms%20of%20White%20Lung%20Syndrome%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFever%3Cbr%3E%5CnCough%3Cbr%3E%5CnShortness%20of%20breath%3Cbr%3E%5CnChest%20pain%3Cbr%3E%5CnFatigue%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701427860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Ff6bucdmg_hospital-generic-650_625x300_06_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmysterious-white-lung-syndrome-spreads-globally-cases-reported-worldwide-4624209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20strain%20of%20bacterial%20pneumonia%20has%20emerged%20in%20China%20and%20spread%20to%20Denmark%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%20Children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%203%20and%208%20are%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20this%20respiratory%20illness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmysterious-white-lung-syndrome-spreads-globally-cases-reported-worldwide-4624209%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmysterious-white-lung-syndrome-spreads-globally-cases-reported-worldwide-4624209%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmysterious-white-lung-syndr