urns-earlier-this-year-13019876%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Sinduria%20Baniya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30125739%2FScreenshot-2023-11-30-at-12.56.1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Sinduria%20Baniya%20(176%2C310%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIdentifying%20the%20Sinduria%20Baniya%20group%20is%20not%20a%20difficult%20task%20because%20their%20name%20makes%20their%20job%20obvious.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20sell%20vermillion%20to%20women%20who%20follow%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20are%20married.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20312px)%2085vw%2C%20312px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22312%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22447%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20historical%20account%20as%20to%20when%20the%20tradition%20of%20applying%20vermilion%20first%20started%20in%20this%20country.%20However%2C%20the%20use%20of%20indigo%20during%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%2C%20perhaps%20as%20a%20colouring%20agent%2C%20is%20indicated%20by%20excavated%20remains.%20The%20caste%20group%20may%20have%20originated%20back%20then%20but%20this%20cannot%20be%20claimed%20with%20certainty.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20prepare%20vermilion%20from%20the%20seeds%20obtained%20from%20a%20plant%20called%20Camellia%2C%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20indigo%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20seeds%20obtained%20from%20the%20indigo%20plant.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20there%20was%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20no%20trend%20of%20applying%20vermilion%20among%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20copper%20statue%20of%20a%20dancer%20found%20from%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation%2C%20wearing%20clothes%20that%20look%20very%20different%20from%20what%20women%20wear%20today%2C%20offer%20some%20indications.%20The%20bracelets%20in%20her%20hands%20must%20be%20either%20of%20copper%20or%20of%20shell%20obtained%20from%20the%20sea.%20Even%20today%2C%20bracelets%20made%20of%20conch%20shells%20are%20worn%20by%20married%20women%20in%20north%20and%20east%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20information%20recorded%20about%20this%20caste%20group%20in%20history%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20said%20with%20certainty.%20It%20has%20been%20speculated%20that%20when%20Aryans%20arrived%20in%20this%20country%2C%20they%20must%20have%20asked%20enslaved%20women%20to%20apply%20vermilion.%20The%20Aryans%20themselves%20wear%20a%20sacred%20thread%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaneu%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20keep%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echoti%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(a%20tuft%20of%20hair)%2C%20with%20which%20they%20are%20identified.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20notion%20of%20slavery%20also%20gains%20ground%20from%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20Aryan%20Brahmin%20epic%2C%20which%20mentions%20that%20Hanuman%20applied%20red%20vermillion%20paste%20on%20his%20body%20as%20a%20proof%20of%20his%20servitude%20towards%20his%20master%20Ram.%20However%2C%20this%20text%20also%20states%20that%20someone%20told%20Hanuman%20that%20since%20Sita%20is%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20wife%20and%20applies%20vermilion%20in%20his%20name%2C%20she%20is%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eservant.%20Upon%20hearing%20this%2C%20Hanuman%20replied%20that%20Sita%20applies%20vermillion%20only%20in%20the%20parting%20of%20her%20hair%20while%20he%20paints%20his%20entire%20body%20red.%20A%20verse%20from%20%3Cem%3EHanuman%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EChalisa%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20states%20that%20the%20one%20who%20turned%20his%20body%20red%20with%20vermilion%2C%20that%20is%20Hanuman%2C%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Lal%20Langur%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESinduria%3C%2Fspan%3E%20B%3Cspan%3Eaniyas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egrow%20camellia%20plants%20and%20prepare%20vermillion%20by%20drying%20the%20fruits%20obtained%20from%20it.%20Once%20dried%2C%20women%20in%20the%20S%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Einduria%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehouseholds%20help%20in%20grinding%20it%20finely.%20The%20vermillion%20thus%20obtained%20is%20then%20sold%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESinduriya%20Baniyas%20are%20different%20from%20most%20Baniyas%20because%20they%20make%20the%20products%20they%20sell.%20They%20are%20also%20distinct%20from%20Jogis%20and%20Churihars%2C%20though%20all%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20a%20community%20which%20furnishes%20symbols%20of%20matrimony%20to%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESinduria%20Baniyas%20are%20also%20different%20from%20other%20Baniyas%20in%20their%20disavowal%20of%20caste%20division.%20They%20have%20provided%20vermillion%20to%20all%20women%20irrespective%20of%20caste.%20On%20this%20basis%2C%20their%20work%20can%20be%20called%20noble.%20This%20is%20why%20even%20today%20when%20things%20are%20getting%20costlier%20by%20the%20day%2C%20vermillion%20never%20seems%20to%20become%20expensive.%20The%20community%20have%20seldom%20indulged%20in%20black%20marketing%20or%20hoarding.%20They%20are%20also%20called%20Kathbaniya%20which%20literally%20means%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbaniya%20only%20in%20name.%E2%80%9D%20In%20Bihar%20they%20were%20also%20called%20Kaithal%20Vaishya.%20In%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20again%2C%20they%20were%20called%20Sinduria%20Baniya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20is%20176%2C310.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20two%20problems%20with%20this%20number.%20First%2C%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20now%20want%20to%20avoid%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20Sinduria%20Bania%20because%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20form%20matrimonial%20alliances%20with%20affluent%20Bania%20families.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20being%20a%20Sinduria%20has%20become%20a%20stigma%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20on%20April%205%2C%202013%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20removed%20this%20caste%20group%20from%20the%20list%20of%20prosperous%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20castes%20(Schedule-2)%20and%20included%20them%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Extremely%20Backward%20Castes%20(Schedule-1).%20Since%20then%2C%20people%20from%20other%20castes%20of%20the%20Baniya%20community%20have%20also%20obtained%20caste%20certificates%20identifying%20themselves%20as%20Sinduria%20Bania.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20their%20traditional%20profession%20is%20also%20in%20dire%20straits%20as%20big%20companies%20have%20now%20entered%20the%20market%20as%20vermillion%20manufacturers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261392%2Fbihar-caste-survey-sinduria-baniya-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%5C%22%3ERangrez%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chamar%5C%22%3EChamar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-gorkan%5C%22%3EGorkan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbi